title: Dr. Bombay & Dr. MacDoo - The Hits (Collection with the best hit
description:
Dr. Bombay + Dr. MacDoo - The Hits,
a collection-album from 2007.
Including the previous unreleased song Spice It Up, the Calcutta 2008 Basshunter Remix and videos.

This is exactly what you get when you buy the album.
So... Enjoy! :)

All the music is in MP3 - 320 kbit/s - 44.1 Khz (perfect quality).
